{"tid":840163,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[Kpop] 4大主舞一齊回歸","createTime":"2018-09-28T13:08:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-28T13:09:46.000Z","uid":152432,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"f358876957995135aa73fc8ff80a2c047e2fa12b","tid":840163,"uid":152432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T13:08:24.000Z","msg":"「STATION X 0」企劃的第四波音源由Red Velvet成員澀琪、GFRIEND成員SinB、金請夏、(G)I-DLE成員田小娟合唱的「Wow Thing」將於28日公開。她們表示很高興可以參與此次的合作，讓她們有機會嘗試了更多不同色彩的音樂。<br />\n「SM STATION」是SM娛樂找來多方藝人、製作人、作曲家合作，每週推出全新音樂作品的企劃。該企劃的第三季「STATION X 0」於今年8月找來太妍和 MeloMance合作《Page 0》時，就已造成話題。<br />\n「STATION X 0」的第二輪合作計畫，邀請了EXO的伯賢及饒舌歌手Loco合作，於8月31日推出《YOUNG》，本月14日又以EXO的燦烈及世勳的組合推出《We Young》。今日又再宣布瑟琪、SinB（信飛）、請夏及田小娟將於9月28日推出《Wow Thing》<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KR5CtMLuiqQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DKR5CtMLuiqQ&d=D7p7yELdsgYnL284KuL%2F7BOFz4pMHIf1Ti9x7C0XgVU%3D&h=470b0de3\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KR5CtMLuiqQ</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/28/210104_40bc86dd76a3ab5c76a800850e6a3bd9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F28%2F210104_40bc86dd76a3ab5c76a800850e6a3bd9.jpg&h=388b78ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/28/210106_a56575f34b61b66e43a76147029e5ff3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F28%2F210106_a56575f34b61b66e43a76147029e5ff3.jpg&h=0aa51b4d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/28/210108_4f41d7d18103da8bde05ac8d7e1a176d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F28%2F210108_4f41d7d18103da8bde05ac8d7e1a176d.jpg&h=3ebf21bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔知係咪因為SM搞定個Concept問題,澀琪係4人中好鬼突出,最型最索最靚但唔會話好突登好造作,閪下閪下跳下舞比D甜頭你再黑